  "detailed_description": "The Pioneers: Surviving Desolation is an innovative space simulation game where you play as a crew of specialists that must survive and explore the secrets of the desolated moon, Io.<br><br>Planet Earth. 2084. It is time to put your mark on history. You are in charge of Io-1, the first inhabited space mission to Io. The dangerous biomes here feature extreme temperatures, intense volcanic and seismic activity and magnetic storms. Retrieve your space station, prep your crew, manage your resources and get ready to face the most hostile environments in the solar system.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/829b2812c6fdcc4d5833e5c16fd1c5ff.avif?t=1715636885\" width=640 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/4e7329a38c75bfd9bc88a1a08bc834ba.poster.avif?t=1715636885\" width=650 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/4e7329a38c75bfd9bc88a1a08bc834ba.webm?t=1715636885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/4e7329a38c75bfd9bc88a1a08bc834ba.mp4?t=1715636885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each game of The Pioneers offers players a unique challenge. Start with 3 different characters chosen randomly among a pool of 15. Adapt to their strengths and weaknesses and use everything they have at their disposal to survive. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/5ad32045310c19cc3962d7b0fcf71f8f.avif?t=1715636885\" width=640 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/fbbe21a7f2022e0b089565a76cfc7637.poster.avif?t=1715636885\" width=650 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/fbbe21a7f2022e0b089565a76cfc7637.webm?t=1715636885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/fbbe21a7f2022e0b089565a76cfc7637.mp4?t=1715636885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Your spaceship has wrecked on the surface of Io but you can still use the parts to your advantage. Produce Materials, build modules and engineering systems, craft wearable equipment and make food. Utilize the game’s advanced health system to monitor everyone carefully to keep them alive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/085074e077745c05053ba9db10a28ed8.avif?t=1715636885\" width=640 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/0dfe827af1ef7f5edece1b248b984c87.poster.avif?t=1715636885\" width=650 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/0dfe827af1ef7f5edece1b248b984c87.webm?t=1715636885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/0dfe827af1ef7f5edece1b248b984c87.mp4?t=1715636885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Volcanos, seismic activity and magnetic storms will put nearly constant pressure on your crew. Monitor your beacons carefully to avoid dying because of a sulfur wind. Anticipate and adapt. Your life depends on it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/40bf4ffb19575d4adeb120f46a70cda9.avif?t=1715636885\" width=640 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/3b7682f7509487475f65a91e7ad9023e.poster.avif?t=1715636885\" width=640 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/3b7682f7509487475f65a91e7ad9023e.webm?t=1715636885\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/3b7682f7509487475f65a91e7ad9023e.mp4?t=1715636885\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Io may be dangerous but it is also home to beautiful, desolate landscapes. Board a rover or a flying drone and venture out to gather precious resources int he various biomes of Io. Explore the land and collect important scientific data to accomplish your mission.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A New Adventure to Experience</h2><br><br>The Pioneers: Surviving Desolation features multiple winning conditions and endings. Play again and again, take advantage of upgrades, learn the best strategies for survival, and master all of Io’s unforgiving elements. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras/039bfd97a25263864260741cbf8b3e94.webp?t=1715636885\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734390/extras_big/039bfd97a25263864260741cbf8b3e94.webp?t=1715636885 width=1024 height=40 /></span>",
